3
00:00:07,540 --> 00:00:09,720
Begin with your compassionate posture

4
00:00:10,420 --> 00:00:12,160
Find a comfortable position

5
00:00:13,720 --> 00:00:15,100
You can close your eyes

6
00:00:15,700 --> 00:00:16,800
or just look down

7
00:00:16,940 --> 00:00:18,960
or have an unfocused gaze

8
00:00:21,500 --> 00:00:23,480
Lift your shoulders up and back

9
00:00:24,140 --> 00:00:28,900
and notice how this creates a concave curve in your back that lifts your diaphragm

10
